          <p>There are many use cases where self-hosting server software would
             make sense for your users, yet the burden of managing the server
             environment gets in the way.</p>
          <p>Engines can help. Our mission is to get your software into the
            hands of more users by lowering the technical hurdles faced by
            those that want to self-host.</p>
          <p>On the commercial side, Engines will incorporate a licensing and
             payment system, so that you can get properly rewarded for writing
